# =============================================================================
# Notes for Code Owners
# =============================================================================
#
# Responsibilities:
# - Review pull requests that modify files you own
# - Provide timely feedback (within 2 business days)
# - Ensure changes meet quality standards
# - Verify tests and documentation are updated
# - Check for security implications
#
# When to Request Additional Reviewers:
# - Complex architectural changes
# - Security-sensitive modifications
# - Breaking API changes
# - Large refactoring efforts
#
# Approval Requirements:
# - At least one code owner approval required for all PRs
# - Additional maintainer approval for critical paths
# - See BRANCH_PROTECTION.md for full requirements
